        "pdf": "https://www.wikileaks.org/clinton-emails/Clinton_Email_August_Release/C05774721.pdf",
        "id": 166,
        "from": "Hillary Clinton",
        "body": "UNCLASSIFIED U.S. Department of State Case No. F-2014-20439 Doc No. C05774721 Date: 08/31/2015RELEASE IN PART B6From:\t                              H <hrod17@clintonemail.com     >\nSent:\t                              Friday, May 7, 2010 5:25 PM\nTo:\t                                'ValmoroU@state.gov    '\nSubject:\t                           Re: Maggie\n\n\nI can't remember but don't I have some Karzai event? If not, what is he doing then?\n\n\t    Original MessageFrom: Valmoro, Lona J <ValmoroU@state.gov>\nTo: H; Abedin, Huma <AbedinH@state.gov>\nSent: Fri May 07 17:06:01 2010\nSubject: Maggie\n\n\nMS -- I just spoke to Maggie and she can meet with you/do dinner on Tuesday night around 7pm. That works well on\nyour schedule but of course wanted to double check before locking in with her.\n\nLona Valmoro\nSpecial Assistant to the Secretary of State\n\t\t\t\t"
