        "to": "Lona Valmoro",
        "timestamp": "2010-05-01 06:22",
        "subject": "SCHEDULING",
        "raw": "<div class=\"tab-pane fade in active\" id=\"content\"><header id=\"header\">\n\t\t\t\t\tFrom: <span title=\"Original: Hillary Clinton\">Hillary Clinton</span>\n\t\t\t\t\tTo: <span title=\"Original: ValmoroLJ@state.gov\">Lona Valmoro</span>\n\t\t\t\t\tDate: 2010-05-01 06:22\n\t\t\t\t\tSubject: SCHEDULING\n\t\t\t\t</header><div class=\"email-content\" id=\"uniquer\"><span class=\"unclassified\">UNCLASSIFIED U.S. Department of State Case No. F-2014-20439 Doc No. C05774616 Date: 08/31/2015</span><span class=\"unclassified\">RELEASE IN FULL</span><span class=\"inlinemeta\">From:\t                              H <hrod17@clintonemail.com>\n</span><span class=\"inlinemeta\">Sent:\t                              Sunday, May 2, 2010 1:22 PM\nTo:\t                                'ValmoroU@state.gov'; Huma Abedin\n</span><span class=\"inlinemeta\">Subject:\t                           Scheduling\n</span>\n\nHere are a few odds and ends:\n\nSince I'm going to the Bahrain Manama Conf in December, I want to decide where else I might go. The. climate conf in\n\nMexico will be held Nov 29-Dec 10. There is also a Dec 10 conf on trafficking in Luxor sponsored by Mrs. Mubarak that\nMelanne hopes I could attend.\n\nAdd to list of meetings the following--\n\nRon Kirk\n\nHilda Solis\nWalter Isaacsonï¿½high priority\n\nSandy Levin\nLoretta Sanchez\n\nMax Baucus\nEliot Engel\n\nBen Cardin wants me to come give a speech about the 35th anniversary of the Helsinki Accords on the Hill so I thought If\n\nI'm going back to Helsinki for a speech about the Helinski Accords in July maybe I should do the Hill speech around that\ntime.\n\nAlso, Cheryl wants a staff retreat/meeting so what about May 14 or 28?\n\nDid you get info about the Vietnam symposium the State historian, Carland, invited me to open on 9/29?\n\nI want to plan to go to the Arctic Council in Greenland next April.\n\nDid you find out when Cong Reyes's conf on border security was in August?\n\t\t\t\t</div></div>",
        "pdf": "https://www.wikileaks.org/clinton-emails/Clinton_Email_August_Release/C05774616.pdf",
        "id": 167,
        "from": "Hillary Clinton",
        "body": "UNCLASSIFIED U.S. Department of State Case No. F-2014-20439 Doc No. C05774616 Date: 08/31/2015RELEASE IN FULLFrom:\t                              H <hrod17@clintonemail.com>\nSent:\t                              Sunday, May 2, 2010 1:22 PM\nTo:\t                                'ValmoroU@state.gov'; Huma Abedin\nSubject:\t                           Scheduling\n\n\nHere are a few odds and ends:\n\nSince I'm going to the Bahrain Manama Conf in December, I want to decide where else I might go. The. climate conf in\n\nMexico will be held Nov 29-Dec 10. There is also a Dec 10 conf on trafficking in Luxor sponsored by Mrs. Mubarak that\nMelanne hopes I could attend.\n\nAdd to list of meetings the following--\n\nRon Kirk\n\nHilda Solis\nWalter Isaacsonï¿½high priority\n\nSandy Levin\nLoretta Sanchez\n\nMax Baucus\nEliot Engel\n\nBen Cardin wants me to come give a speech about the 35th anniversary of the Helsinki Accords on the Hill so I thought If\n\nI'm going back to Helsinki for a speech about the Helinski Accords in July maybe I should do the Hill speech around that\ntime.\n\nAlso, Cheryl wants a staff retreat/meeting so what about May 14 or 28?\n\nDid you get info about the Vietnam symposium the State historian, Carland, invited me to open on 9/29?\n\nI want to plan to go to the Arctic Council in Greenland next April.\n\nDid you find out when Cong Reyes's conf on border security was in August?\n\t\t\t\t"
