        "pdf": "https://www.wikileaks.org/clinton-emails/Clinton_Email_August_Release/C05775521.pdf",
        "id": 224,
        "from": "Hillary Clinton",
        "body": "UNCLASSIFIED U.S. Department of State Case No. F-2014-20439 Doc No. C05775521 Date: 08/31/2015RELEASE IN FULLFrom:\t                             H <hrod17@clintonemail.com>\nSent:\t                             Sunday, April 25, 2010 11:12 AM\nTo:\t                               'bam@mikulski.senate.gov   '\nSubject:\t                          Good luck on a good start!\n\n\nBarb--\n\n  I loved your comments at your re-election kickoff and hope you've scared off all the would-be opponents.\n\n  How's our friend, Martin, doing? I know he has a rematch when he should be reelected by acclamation for steering the\nship of state so well. Pls give him my best wishes.\n\n  And go get 'em! Your friend and booster, Hillary\n\t\t\t\t"
