        "body": "UNCLASSIFIED U.S. Department of State Case No. F-2014-20439 Doc No. C05775053 Date: 08/31/2015RELEASE IN PART\n                                                                                                                  B6\n\n       \t                                                                 >\nFrom: \t                                H <hrod17@clintonemail.com\nSent:                                  Thursday, April 22, 2010 9:20 AM\nTo:      \t                             'muscatinel@state.gov'\nSubject:                               Re: betsey griffith\n\n\n                                                                                                          Any chance the date could\t              B6\n\nbe changed?\n\n\t    Original MessageFrom: Muscatine, Lissa <MuscatineL@state.gov          >\nTo: H\nSent: Thu Apr 22 09:01:37 2010\nSubject: betsey griffith\n\n\nSheepishly inquired as to whether you might be willing to speak at Madeira's commencement on June 4th in the\nmorning. It's her last time officiating as head of the school. It's a couple of days before the Lat Am trip. Thoughts?\n\t\t\t\t"
